              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "In Power BI, for most visuals, there are three kinds of Visual Interactions, ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Highlight",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": ", ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Filter ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "and ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "None. ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "By default, interactions are set to Highlight, but often users prefer to ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Filter",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": ".  ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "It is also worth checking if the "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Use modern visual header with updated styling options ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "option is enabled. When this is turned off, visuals will display a grey bar across the top, which can be used for selecting and moving the visual, but will mean no visual can be set to the top of the canvas. Additionally, object grouping in the Selection Pane will not persist.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "To change the default, go to ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "File > Options and Settings > Options > Current File, Report Settings ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "and check the box ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Change default visual interaction from cross highlighting to cross filtering ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "and",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "turn on the ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Use modern visual header with updated styling options.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#767676"
                    }
                  }
